deHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=da2aac3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"},{"pid":"4693f86d19a4f6b23db5e477701554c18b97aec0","tid":1578426,"uid":306925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:57:46.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"c2359e2cb5083473e01c4560e199f048e135cdd0","tid":1578426,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"276cfd36ab87feb40137fccb7c11cdaac25e9c97","tid":1578426,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d3091420ab9637ec2b0ce972942a0686c642bc8","tid":1578426,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cd95e079ad7c6127773adcf32815babb50237fe","tid":1578426,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"統計數據從來只會反映整體的客觀事實，並不會成為任何論述的助燃劑。除了實質證據能告訴我們事實真相，其他數字都只能作為一般參考。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7Q6zgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7Q6zgV.jpg&h=3f4d19c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=37153639\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=9439362f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=da2aac3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>[/quote]"}]}